Class FormService

java.lang.Object
pl.edu.pwr.pkuchnowski.filltheformapi.service.FormService
@Service public class FormService extends Object
Service class for getting Google Form responses. Uses the GoogleFormGetter class to get the form response.

  • Method Details

    • getGoogleFormResponse

      public com.google.api.services.script.model.Operation getGoogleFormResponse(String formId, String accessToken, String firstName, String lastName, String email, String phone, String orderNumber, String orderDate, String[] orderElements, String[] elementQuantities) throws GeneralSecurityException, IOException
      Gets the Google Form response.
      Parameters:
      formId - The ID of the Google Form.
      accessToken - The access token obtained from Google OAuth2.
      firstName - The first name of the customer.
      lastName - The last name of the customer.
      email - The email address of the customer.
      phone - The phone number of the customer.
      orderNumber - The order number.
      orderDate - The order date.
      orderElements - The elements of the order.
      elementQuantities - The quantities of the elements.
      Returns:
      The Google Form response.
      Throws:
      GeneralSecurityException - If a security error occurs.
      IOException - If an I/O error occurs.
